.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, may, june, august
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, epic, zombie, superhero
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person watching epic movies##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##8
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5

